               <th class=''center''><i class="fa fa-check"></i></th>\r\n                    <td>Document management</td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                    <th class=''center''><i class="fa fa-check"></i></th>\r\n                    <td>Calendaring for meetings</td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                    <th class=''center''><i class="fa fa-check"></i></th>\r\n                    <td>Committee management</td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                    <th class=''center''><i class="fa fa-check"></i></th>\r\n                    <td>Management of capitalization table</td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                    <th class=''center''><i class="fa fa-check"></i></th>\r\n                    <td>Single sign on to a consolidated dashboard with all the companies you are involved in</td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            <div class=''clearfix''></div>\r\n            <h2>KoreConX Private Label Program</h2>\r\n            <p>KoreConX offers a unique private label program for law firms.</p>\r\n            <p>KoreConX is currently in 44 countries and is being used by private, public and non-profit organizations.</p>\r\n            <p>Our private label program will provide training for you to fully understand how to use KoreConX and how to implement it with your clients in a way that allows you to efficiently manage them.  This will enhance your practice by providing you with a broader service offering.</p>\r\n            <h3>KoreConX Private Label</h3>\r\n            <p>KoreConX private label program provides your law firm with the ability to offer KoreConX to your current and future clients under your own brand and login page.</p>\r\n            <p>The private label program is designed for those firms that want to retain their brand with clients and still offer a world-class application.</p>\r\n            <p>The private label program will have branded URL so your clients can register and login through your site.</p>\r\n            <h3>Why Private Label</h3>\r\n            <ul class=''check-list''>\r\n                <li>Branded URL for your law firm</li>\r\n                <li>Provides your law firm greater stickiness to your clients with your brand creating further barrier for your competitors to gain access to your clients</li>\r\n                <li>Enhanced client retention</li>\r\n                <li>Provides your clients access to additional services such as (insurance, background checks, corporate registry, newswire, etc.) through KoreConX</li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n            <h3>Requirements</h3>\r\n            <ul class=''check-list''>\r\n                <li>Have a valid URL company website</li>\r\n                <li>Maintain an annual SSL Certificate</li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n            <p>If you are interested in KoreConX’s Private Label Program please fill out our online application.</p>\r\n<div id="application-form" class="contact lightbox">[contact-form-7 id="644" title="Application Form"]</div>', 'Private Label for Law Firms', '<p>KoreConX supports private companies, non-profits, listed issuers, and all key stakeholders by providing a platform to manage, organize, share, and communicate all their corporate activities.  Our platform facilitates the management of all three phases, pre-during-post, of crowdfunding and capital markets transactions.  The platform facilitates due diligence of issuers, data repository/deal room and shareholder management/communications.</p>\r\n\r\n            <p>KoreConX partners with law firms to provide our platform on a private label basis for your clients to sign in directly through your law firms website.</p>\r\n\r\n            <p>Organizations are struggling with an ever-increasing burden of managing regulation, compliance and reporting regardless of their status as a public, private or not-for-profit (NPO) entity. Many use applications designed for very different requirements to manage corporate information, often transferring critical documents without sufficient security, such as sending documents to unprotected external email addresses or mail systems. KoreConX brings deep industry and business process proficiency to a number of segments within the industry including compliance, corporate record keeping and management, listings, government filings, registry requirements and shareholder communications.  For example, KoreConX has developed its data management and communications solution to reduce risk and costs and allow the Board of any entity to spend their time guiding rather than on compliance.</p>\r\n\r\n            <p>To ensure good governance and reduce regulatory risks, boards have to be involved in with Managing, Organizing and Sharing.</p>\r\n            <blockquote>\r\n                <p>I believe that KoreConX provides real value to our company and our shareholders.  For us it provides an integrated, secure, transparent and efficient way for the management of WAFU to interact with its shareholders and its board of directors.  The time and costs saving alone make it a no brainer for a small company like ours which currently has 20-30 shareholders but which is expecting to expand to more than 50 shareholders as a result of our upcoming equity crowdfunding round. </p>\r\n                <footer>Gil-Michel Garcia  |  CEO  |  WAFU</footer>\r\n            </blockquote>\r\n            <p>KoreConX plays a key role by helping issuers (both private and public) organize their corporate and financial information for due diligence. Our platform provides the ability for issuers to pre-screen principal players with background checks, corporate searches, etc. At the post transaction level, all of the closing documents and shareholder information is automatically uploaded into the KoreConX system. This provides regulated access to  closing documents, share certificates/registers, and any information an issuer is required to share with its shareholders and stakeholders, all in a secure environment accessible online. KoreConX brings issuers and shareholders together like no other environment that exists today.  Whether as a legal services provider or as a corporate secretary service, KoreConX allows for enhanced service offerings:</p>\r\n            <h2>KoreConX Security</h2>\r\n            <p>KoreConX recognizes that corporate data is the most one of the most valuable assets held by any business.  For that reason, KoreConX provides the highest standards of encryption, controls, and security for the collection, transmission and storage of data.</p>\r\n            <p>KoreConX is certified by TRUSTe and VeriSign, the KoreConX platform is hosted in a SSAE Type 16 and ISO 27001 certified environment.</p>\r\n            <div class=''center''><img src=''http://koreconx.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/chart.jpg'' class=''img-responsive''/></div>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'legal', '', '', '2015-01-17 12:48:50', '2015-01-17 12:48:50', '', 640, 'http://koreconx.com/?page_id=638', 0, 'page', '', 0),
