X Certified Trainer</li>\r\n                <li>You can add our KoreConX Certified Trainer Seal on your site</li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n            <h3>Requirements</h3>\r\n            <ul class=''check-list''>\r\n                <li>Pass KoreConX Certified Expert Program (CEP)</li>\r\n                <li>Participate in KoreConX on going training program</li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n            <p>KoreConX provides you full training and referrals in your region.</p>\r\n            <p>If you are interested in becoming a KoreConX Certified Expert take a moment to fill out the CEP Application.</p>\r\n<div id="certified-application-form" class="contact lightbox">[contact-form-7 id="656" title="Certified Expert Program"]</div>', 'Certified Expert Program', '<p>KoreConX supports private companies, non-profits, listed issuers, and all key stakeholders by providing a platform to manage, organize, share, and communicate all their corporate activities.  Our platform facilitates the management of all three phases, pre-during-post, of crowdfunding and capital markets transactions.  The platform facilitates due diligence of issuers, data repository/deal room and shareholder management/communications.</p>\r\n\r\n            <p>KoreConX brings deep industry and business process proficiency to a number of segments within the industry including compliance, corporate record keeping and management, listings, government filings, registry requirements and shareholder communications. Organizations are struggling with an ever-increasing burden of regulation, compliance and reporting being applied to them regardless of their status as a public, private or not-for-profit (NPO) entity. Many use applications designed for very different requirements to manage corporate information, often transferring critical documents without sufficient security, such as sending documents to unprotected external email addresses or mail systems. KoreConX has developed its data management and communications solution to reduce risk and costs and allow the directors of any entity to spend their time on guidance rather than compliance.</p>\r\n\r\n            <p>Directors on Boards have significant risks and responsibilities. KoreConX was created to mitigate risk by providing directors and officers a simple yet powerful solution to address their responsibilities surrounding good governance and compliance.  It all starts with Managing, Organizing and Sharing.</p>\r\n\r\n            <blockquote>\r\n                <p>I believe that KoreConX provides real value to our company and our shareholders.  For us it provides an integrated, secure, transparent and efficient way for the management of WAFU to interact with its shareholders and its board of directors.  The time and costs saving alone make it a no brainer for a small company like ours which currently has 20-30 shareholders but which is expecting to expand to more than 50 shareholders as a result of our upcoming equity crowdfunding round.</p>\r\n                <footer>Gil-Michel Garcia  |  CEO  |  WAFU</footer>\r\n            </blockquote>\r\n            <p>KoreConX plays a key role by helping issuers (both private and public) organize their corporate and financial information for due diligence. Our platform provides the ability for issuers to pre-screen principal players with background checks, corporate searches, etc. At the post transaction level, all of the closing documents and shareholder information is automatically uploaded into the KoreConX system. This provides regulated access to  closing documents, share certificates/registers, and any information an issuer is required to share with its shareholders and stakeholders, all in a secure environment accessible online. KoreConX brings issuers and shareholders together like no other environment that exists today.  Whether as a legal services provider or as a corporate secretary service, KoreConX allows for enhanced service offerings:</p>\r\n            <h2>KoreConX Security</h2>\r\n            <p>KoreConX recognizes that corporate data is the most one of the most valuable assets held by any business.  For that reason, KoreConX provides the highest standards of encryption, controls, and security for the collection, transmission and storage of data.</p>\r\n            <p>KoreConX is certified by TRUSTe and VeriSign, the KoreConX platform is hosted in a SSAE Type 16 and ISO 27001 certified environment.</p>\r\n<hr class="line-break"/>\r\n            <div class=''center''><img src=''http://koreconx.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/chart.jpg'' class=''img-responsive''/></div>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'cep', '', '', '2015-03-17 09:19:41', '2015-03-17 09:19:41', '', 640, 'http://koreconx.com/?page_id=655', 0, 'page', '', 0),
